                  <td width="455" valign="top" bgcolor="#FFFFFF" class="style2"><p>Steve Mills, chairman of the IEEE standards board,  responding to allegations of favoritism shown to QualComm by 802.20 Chair Jerry  Upton<a href="http://www.eetimes.com/news/latest/showArticle.jhtml?articleID=189401737">...Full Story</a></p></td>
