                <tr>
                  <td colspan="2" valign="top" bgcolor="#FFFFFF" class="style2"><p><strong><em>Skeptical but intrigued</em></strong><em>&nbsp;&nbsp;[June  15, 2006]</em></p></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td width="46" valign="top" bgcolor="#FFFFFF" class="style2">&nbsp;</td>
                  <td width="455" valign="top" bgcolor="#FFFFFF" class="style2"><p>Bob Muglia,  Microsoft's SVP of server and tools, describing the reaction of the open source  community to Microsoft's new interoperability initiatives<a href="http://www.eweek.com/article2/0%2C1895%2C1977468%2C00.asp">...Full Story</a></p></td>
